snippet.title: Note Ban: Rahul Gandhi Meets Road-side Vendors in Delhi

localized.description:
Demonetisation of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 Notes: Congress vice-president Rahul Gandhi meets road-side vendors in Delhi. Opposition parties Congress, TMC, Left and AAP are opposing Modi government over ban on currency notes of Rs 500 and 1000
